        "type": "text",
        "text": "General product information:",
        "text_level": 2,
        "bbox": [
            70,
            61,
            307,
            76
        ],
        "page_idx": 6
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Product covered by this report is grid-connected PV inverter for indoor or outdoor installation. The connection to the DC input and AC output are through connectors.",
        "bbox": [
            68,
            79,
            904,
            108
        ],
        "page_idx": 6
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "The Solar inverter converts DC voltage into AC voltage.",
        "bbox": [
            70,
            119,
            487,
            134
        ],
        "page_idx": 6
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "The input and output are protected by varistors to Earth. The unit is providing EMC filtering at the output toward mains. The unit does not provide galvanic separation from input to output (transformerless). The output is switched off redundant by the high-power switching bridge and two relays. This assures that the opening of the output circuit can operate in case of single fault.",
        "bbox": [
            68,
            133,
            927,
            187
        ],
        "page_idx": 6
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Equipment Under Testing:",
        "text_level": 2,
        "bbox": [
            70,
            200,
            282,
            214
        ],
        "page_idx": 6
    },
    {
